race.comment: HOT MAJESTY (1) just ran into one better over this course and distance last time out and looks to be working up to another victory. Ready to peak now fourth run back and gets some weight relief with the 2kg claim. Should be right there when the whips are cracking. SEXY TIME (3) has come back in good order with a win and two placings from three runs this campaign and may have turned the corner now. Looks well placed here so expect another forward showing. ZEAMAIZE (2) has a win and a placing from two spins around this circuit and is drawn to get all the favours from the inside alley. Top-three conveyance. POSSIBILITIES (7) has hit the top-four at her past 11 starts and is usually thereabouts. One for the exotics players. DASHING MARS (9) is a last-start winner who shouldn't be slept on.
